== GOAL

ScripIT is a Python skeleton to speed up "post installation" script development

== FUNCTIONS

= showexec(description, command, exitonerror = 0)
Display and exec a shell function

Output exemple:
File list                                                             [  OK   ]
A very very very long description for this little command too lon...  [  OK   ]
Noexist command but continue                                          [Warning]
Wait 1 second                                                         [  OK   ]
Noexist command but quit                                              [ Error ]

= getpassword(description = "")
Get a password from the CLI
